Description: 

    The Django-hotsauce toolkit is a experimental Python web framework based on
    WSGI 1.0 and Django 1.0.

    == Features ==

    * Native Schevo ORM and ZODB storage backend 
    * High-performance PyPy (JIT) and Python 3.7 support on top of WSGI 1.0
    * Enhanced nginx and uWSGI support 
    * Generic authorization and authentication support (oauthlib, libauthkit) 
    * Experimental gevent support
    * Commercial licenses available
    * etc...
